<p><a title="" name="_ftn9" href="#_ftnref9"> [9] </a> In June 2015, M<sup>3</sup>AAWG and LAP published Operation Safety-Net: Best Practices to address online, mobile and telephony threats, https://www.m3aawg.org/sites/default/files/M3AAWG_LAP-79652_IC_Operation-Safety-Net_2-BPs2015-06.pdf.</p>
